<item>
            <title>[FLINK-8687] MaterializedCollectStreamResult#retrievePage should take resultLock</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-8687</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently MaterializedCollectStreamResult#retrievePage checks page range and calls snapshot.subList() without holding resultLock.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;resultLock&lt;/tt&gt; should be taken.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13139261">FLINK-8687</key>
            <summary>MaterializedCollectStreamResult#retrievePage should take resultLock</summary>
