	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;    Currently ```MaterializedCollectStreamResult#retrievePage``` checks page range and calls snapshot.subList() without holding resultLock. resultLock should be taken.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;ol&gt;
